Definition: correct to the last detail
Example: especially being in or following the exact words; a letter-perfect rendition of the soliloquy; she was word-perfect in her part
Synonyms: word-perfect, correct, to, the, last, detail, especially, being, in, or, following, exact, words, a, rendition, of, soliloquy, she, was, her, part
Category: adj.all
